{"tid":1119932,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有無巴打喺泰國知道清邁星期六係咪落暴雨搞到好大件事？","createTime":"2019-04-22T09:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T08:34:32.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abbd851f960bb09e072fd36ccb94eefbacd35898","tid":1119932,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友喺當地話停電 嗰陣我以為果啲地方會停電係好平常 跟住當晚佢話有返電又同佢傾左一陣<br />\n<br />\n點知第二日即係星期日 到今日佢都無再on過line<br />\n<br />\n之後我再google睇新聞先發現原來係暴雨搞到清邁果邊好多個縣受損又有好多房屋受破壞搞到停電咁樣 大家覺得我可以點做？ 我好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16ee805070df52c5b7d5513fa54135735afd001","tid":1119932,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"依家好唔安樂<br />\n如果佢係停電而無Wi-Fi上唔到都算<br />\n如果係另一種&hellip;&hellip; 我唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我依家直頭想喊"},{"pid":"9e72841ccef7ba49cf79503dcf75c813b06c46b6","tid":1119932,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"負評果條傻柒我唔會理你<br />\n我只係想知我朋友係咪平安<br />\n希望你有一日會覆返我 我真係好驚好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1872078dfaaa2c220aab41cba6b563cd822a2aef","tid":1119932,"uid":74927,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:47:44.000Z","msg":"想我嬲？"},{"pid":"daba80f877aa72fe63594caa2e191840899015b0"